{"tid":2254484,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【Cookies18周年】區文詩大閘蟹宴為鄧麗欣慶祝生日 愈住愈豪搬入3千萬西半山豪宅","createTime":"2020-10-23T00:50:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T04:30:03.000Z","uid":71166,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"44fc5c3ecb18bf6bff2aa456665656c70b64330c","tid":2254484,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T00:50:09.000Z","msg":"10月15日是鄧麗欣 (Stephy）37歲生日，雖然男朋友王子邱勝翊身在台灣未能一起慶祝，不過Stephy都不愁寂寞，連日來跟不同朋友開派對慶祝，非常熱鬧。而前Cookies好姊妹區文詩為Stephy一次過準備四個大蛋糕，認真大陣仗！除了蛋糕之外，還有時令大閘蟹，她們一邊傾偈敘舊，一邊大快朵頤 ; 而原來區文詩已經連續兩年跟Stephy吃以大閘蟹宴來慶祝生日，絕對是「蟹粉」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3xytSMi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3xytSMi.png&h=5a218adf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f430749bb3cdc4f79daaf3ec264b207ea480537e","tid":2254484,"uid":71166,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T00:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w8ONoS8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw8ONoS8.png&h=0129ebef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uRJtSMu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuRJtSMu.png&h=22d8dbdb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03d74b63af54b3e8d5baa0f9d3263d4c5d4cd0ea","tid":2254484,"uid":71166,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T00:51:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/62q4q6E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F62q4q6E.jpg&h=630e8dcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/054T3Tk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F054T3Tk.jpg&h=1a8d9821&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7b780085e5565f8f67823a4e3120d48b5a263e6","tid":2254484,"uid":34571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T00:52:24.000Z","msg":"通常一堆女一定有個tb"},{"pid":"fa4be31d65ad618f457b003d6b3746728a7f35ca","tid":2254484,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T00:52:38.000Z","msg":"「餅碎」之一的區文詩雖然早於Cookies第一輪重組時已經被淘汰，不過她跟骨幹成員吳雨霏、鄧麗欣和楊愛瑾都非常老友。自近年離開香港電台的DJ工作，她已甚少在熒幕前露面，卻被踢爆愈住愈豪，而且IG全部都是旅行的照片，生活相當富泰。<br />\n<br />\n一向揚言「只愛磚頭」的區文詩投資有道，2013年2月以452.2萬購入大角咀奧城‧西岸1房戶，直至去年5月以542萬沽出。同月她購入西半山年豐園一個頂層連天台單位，連車位以3,380萬元售出，上址實用面積1,194方呎，呎價28,308元。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QrV78kv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQrV78kv.png&h=55b5bb33&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c64f58519bb287c1bb1dc85a8ef0429d42a3c74","tid":2254484,"uid":71166,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c7b780085e5565f8f67823a4e3120d48b5a263e6","tid":2254484,"uid":34571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T00:52:24.000Z","msg":"通常一堆女一定有個tb"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T00:53:06.000Z","msg":"呢樣真 仲要係有米TB唔知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8260be7acbfe7a489529d87aac96cfc53d0dfeb","tid":2254484,"uid":71166,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"c7b780085e5565f8f67823a4e3120d48b5a263e6","tid":2254484,"uid":34571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T00:52:24.000Z","msg":"通常一堆女一定有個tb"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T00:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gXp8SNR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgXp8SNR.png&h=772947fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b55e435426e0cc1478b85fdcba07acee16afa081","tid":2254484,"uid":154907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T00:55:27.000Z","msg":"歐盟詩個樣呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3185675a17c0e770fa4198ddf04aabea8afd392","tid":2254484,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8260be7acbfe7a489529d87aac96cfc53d0dfeb","tid":2254484,"uid":71166,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"c7b780085e5565f8f67823a4e3120d48b5a263e6","tid":2254484,"uid":34571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T00:52:24.000Z","msg":"通常一堆女一定有個tb"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T00:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gXp8SNR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgXp8SNR.png&h=772947fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T00:57:20.000Z","msg":"stephy張大合照本身有個tb"},{"pid":"3b82c6617f16983f3017996452de9711c1ee6e9a","tid":2254484,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T00:58:25.000Z","msg":"區文詩在社交平台有不少新居的照片，無論是客飯廳還是天台，都分別招呼過不少朋友。照片中所見，飯廳有張長長的雲石枱，可以容納6至8人一齊食飯。飯枱前方是大梳化和貼櫃的大電視，而疑似廚房位置有吧枱，亦設有吧枱椅可以跟朋友吃飯飲酒。至於天台位置，由於位於半山較高的位置，望到的都是大廈的頂部，沒有高樓大廈的壓迫感，被綠意盎然包圍，景色怡人。<br />\n<br />\n一向入得廚房的區文詩早前轉戰做YouTuber，跟不同圈中好友煮餸，煮得有板有眼。難怪她在新居頻頻招呼朋友食飯。<img src=\"https://p9-bk.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-mlhdmxsy5m/c49aff019d974ed6a36499a9c325d789~tplv-mlhdmxsy5m-q75:1080:1080.image\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp9-bk.byteimg.com%2Ftos-cn-i-mlhdmxsy5m%2Fc49aff019d974ed6a36499a9c325d789~tplv-mlhdmxsy5m-q75%3A1080%3A1080.image&h=5577dd51&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1e3a105c69605864821409b26178967aba42da8","tid":2254484,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b55e435426e0cc1478b85fdcba07acee16afa081","tid":2254484,"uid":154907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T00:55:27.000Z","msg":"歐盟詩個樣呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T01:00:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://p9-bk.byteimg.com/tos-cn