l/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T01:12:02.000Z","msg":"如果冇同Stephy frd，佢有新聞咩？<br />\n每次見報都係有stephy，好難唔錫喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T01:17:23.000Z","msg":"Stephy和Angela更試過同住八年。和其他女孩子一樣，她們的友誼也是在試煉下增長。Angela憶述：「最難忘是有一次和Stephy吵架，因外人講了一些是非，令我們產生誤會。當時一起住又不懂得處理，結果有晚我們家人聚餐，我請她出席，她說沒空，卻被我的朋友見到她獨自去深井吃燒鵝，我知道出了問題，後來在一位共同朋友調解下，才和好如初。不過這件事後，我們學懂了遇到任何事要直接向對方求證，而不是問外人。」<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f9368192b32b269632274637073dcd9b7e6162","tid":2254484,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b55e435426e0cc1478b85fdcba07acee16afa081","tid":2254484,"uid":154907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T00:55:27.000Z","msg":"歐盟詩個樣呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T01:21:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://p9-bk.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-mlhdmxsy5m/b6ad1c00e3a249bead3e3fe88ff9aab1~tplv-mlhdmxsy5m-q75:1080:1080.image\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp9-bk.byteimg.com%2Ftos-cn-i-mlhdmxsy5m%2Fb6ad1c00e3a249bead3e3fe88ff9aab1~tplv-mlhdmxsy5m-q75%3A1080%3A1080.image&h=9637de91&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c95311276ebf1d5a26ca3e093838d780c3b61315","tid":2254484,"uid":56716,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T02:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OodhMwu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOodhMwu.jpg&h=b1656546&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zGYBhDa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzGYBhDa.jpg&h=dfe13cec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tJaPCDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F